| Edge Weights               | Algorithm                     |
| -------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| All edges = 1 (unweighted) | ✅ BFS                         |
| Weights ∈ {0,1}            | ✅ 0-1 BFS                     |
| Weights ≥ 0 (any value)    | ✅ Dijkstra                    |
| Negative weights exist     | ❌ Dijkstra → use Bellman-Ford |


The choice of algorithm depends on edge weights, not on whether the graph is directed or undirected.
